Help on skill: thunderclap
Skill type: special
Usage duration: automatic

With this skill you gain knowledge of moves that disrupt bludgeon
users combat by clapping his arms hard, gaining you the upper hand.

This skill is a part of the martial artists way of combat.
Your skill percent affects how well this skill works.
You need this kata when fighting unarmed against enemy with
some bludgeon. This is the second kata.

